Class DJICameraShutterSpeed

  • java.lang.Object
    • dji.sdk.api.Camera.DJICameraShutterSpeed

  • public class DJICameraShutterSpeed
extends java.lang.Object

    DJI Camera Shutter Speed

    This is a enum class for shutter speed. For helping developer to easily invoke the API correctly, all selections of shutter speed have been packing in this enum class.
    Version:
    V2.4.0
    Author:
    DJI Software
